rulesList.cssText: a { text-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; font-weight: inherit; }

.hero_button-r { position: relative; overflow: hidden; background-color: transparent; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); cursor: pointer; z-index: 1; transition: color 0.3s; }

.hero_button-r::after { content: ""; position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; bottom: 0px; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(transparent 0%, rgb(31, 29, 93) 130%); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s; z-index: -1; }
.nav:has(.nav_dd_trigger.w--open) .nav_blur { display: block; height: 100%; transition: opacity 0.4s; opacity: 1; }
.nav_blur { display: block; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition: opacity 0.4s, visibility 0.4s; }
.nav_burger_content .nav_link { padding-top: 1.5rem; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.063); border-radius: 0px; justify-content: left; }
.nav_burger_content .nav_dd_trigger { padding-top: 1.5rem; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: none; justify-content: space-between; flex-grow: 1; }
